	<p>In June 2019, Koda was adopted from the Rocky Mountain Puppy Rescue team in Colorado.</p>
	<p>A New Mexico native, Koda took to Colorado quickly, and soon found himself loving everything it had to offer, from the snowy mountains to the national parks!</p>
	<p>When the weather permits, Koda is an avid hiker, swimmer, and runner.</p>
